{"tid":1422073,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"覺其實今日狗仔個記招表現都ok啦","createTime":"2019-08-06T09:44:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T10:34:44.000Z","uid":248733,"like":12,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"485880723c19d657de2f53e6d8326acfaf02c7c5","tid":1422073,"uid":248733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:44:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">絕對唔可以high抽水住</span></span><br />\n<br />\n一般市民靠大台接收殘缺資訊<br />\n即使佢地有睇埋記者提問環節<br />\n警方派嘅呢兩個人<br />\n實在比之前一哥同madam YU段數更高<br />\n敢於回應利君雅多次追問<br />\n表現算係不過不失 <span style=\"color: gold;\">甚至可能獲得中上分數</span><br />\n一般人睇完應該會覺得<span style=\"color: gold;\">「警方都叫做盡咗力」</span>（我諗）<br />\n<br />\n睇到呢到 我地仲有時間自high？<br />\n<br />\n民間記者會嘅出現<br />\n代表我地嘅戰爭已經升級到另一階段<br />\n原本嘅要照做<br />\n但呢一條戰線一樣唔可以輕視<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">今日記者仍然會對剛出生嘅三位義士留力<br />\n但聽日 、後日再交唔到令人滿意嘅回答<br />\n記者縱然有心都無力啦<br />\n<br />\n香港人 路遙遙啊</span>"},{"pid":"30c2ca805b9abd6dc3b5b3ac83c4fdd0fa4eea26","tid":1422073,"uid":248733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:45:42.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好掛住自high先啦</span>"},{"pid":"68750f61175d450cad269b360c843689c0f380b9","tid":1422073,"uid":248733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:46:58.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好掛住自high先啦</span>"},{"pid":"401062b0bb71c8cc135934309b3685ed86a684d0","tid":1422073,"uid":248733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:47:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好掛住自high先啦</span>"},{"pid":"894053445a28c4eeb0dbb36f55a29f00220db6dd","tid":1422073,"uid":248733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T09:47:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">唔好掛住自high先啦</span>"},{"pid":"a058b0d287b31fd6ad463cea7bd21f882b51cea6","tid":1422073,"uid":248733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-0